  "body": "Currently the apiserver returns 500 if a patch request contains invalid patch, e.g., if you do `$ kubectl patch -f redis-master.yaml -p feafeczea`, and then check `kube-apiserver.log`, you will see \r\n```\r\nlogging error output: \"{\\\"kind\\\":\\\"Status\\\",\\\"apiVersion\\\":\\\"v1\\\",\\\"metadata\\\":{},\\\"status\\\":\\\"Failure\\\",\\\"message\\\":\\\"json: cannot unmarshal string into Go value of type map[string]interface {}\\\",\\\"code\\\":500}\\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe apiserver should either return a 422 (`NewInvalid`) or a 400 (`NewBadRequest`).\r\n\r\n/kind bug\r\ncc @kubernetes/sig-api-machinery-bugs ",
